{"tid":2172370,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"穿女權字樣白T…YouTuber拍片要Joy「退出Red Velvet」！　韓網譙：你哪根蔥？","createTime":"2020-08-24T14:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T19:38:07.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b84cc7baab2cea51b2e4d6ed835cc97f27174581","tid":2172370,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"南韓女團Red Velvet成員Joy日前在IG曬出了穿著「WE SHOULD ALL BE FEMINISTS」字樣上衣的照片，引發一向對女權主義敏感的各大論壇掀起正面論戰的討論。而近日，一名擁有56萬訂閱的YouTuber「PPKKa」（뻑가）也拍片發表了對事件的看法，直呼「乾脆SOLO活動，別對團員造成困擾」，要求她退出團體。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094484.jpg&h=676b4ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲Joy因穿著印有女權字樣的衣服，引發熱議。（圖／翻攝Joy IG）<br />\n<br />\nPPKKa日前在頻道上傳了標題為「JOY自私的理由」的影片，提及JOY穿著女權主義字樣衣服一事，表示「透過化妝跟衣服造型，對人們展現漂亮、可愛、性感樣貌，以商品性分級別的職業，還敢說『我們都要成為女權主義者』？真了不起，有夠矛盾」， 更直言：「別再對Wendy或澀琪造成負面影響，乾脆像HA:TFELT（譽恩）那樣SOLO活動再喊女權吧。」透露希望JOY退出Red Velvet。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094485.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094485.jpg&h=abc14e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲PPKKa拍攝影片批評Joy。（圖／翻攝YouTube／뻑가）<br />\n<br />\nPPKKa批評JOY的影片上傳後，引起不少網友的憤怒，留言道「JOY有厭男嗎？就只是穿件衣服就說成這樣」、「很多男藝人也穿的衣服」、「這種程度SM（Red Velvet所屬公司）該提告了」、「無知的人還講得頭頭是道」、「我看你是厭女吧ㄎㄎ」、「無言到笑出來」、「你算哪個蔥？」。"},{"pid":"b0055dd4e2fe01d1f0fc69b7d6e8c63a0e5e1896","tid":2172370,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"女權有咩問題"},{"pid":"b1d206b0754506487c67ee98fb4060d634b2808c","tid":2172370,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"乜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891e7d5f14c2dfee979d5e4e2c07a023c4df2e1c","tid":2172370,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"躝啦。"},{"pid":"be0faeade8de45622829718c17e8a999aaba119d","tid":2172370,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1d206b0754506487c67ee98fb4060d634b2808c","tid":2172370,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"乜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"自己SEARCH啦問問問"},{"pid":"f4f2c6561ef5c34ba07f855e0474e1b3fe658bbc","tid":2172370,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"好正常"},{"pid":"e1eb3d2c18f32247a66e96968f1cdaf375d3e0a6","tid":2172370,"uid":188049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T19:38:07.000Z","msg":"比人屌到關閉留言"}]}